image_analysis.description: A financial disclosure document, specifically page A13 of 47 from an OGE Form 278e. The document lists various corporate entities, detailing ownership percentages and roles for the filer, Donald J. Trump. The page is structured as a list with numbered entries from 144 to 154.
image_analysis.layout: The document has a header section with the form number, filer's name, and page number. The main body is a list of entities, each with subsections for 'Owned by' and 'Has ownership interest in', presented in a tabular format without explicit grid lines. A footer at the bottom contains a document identifier.
